query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS cash_flow_projections (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  scenarioId INT NOT NULL,
  year INT NOT NULL,
  capitalExpenditure DECIMAL(15,2) DEFAULT 0,
  maintenanceCost DECIMAL(15,2) DEFAULT 0,
  operatingCost DECIMAL(15,2) DEFAULT 0,
  totalCost DECIMAL(15,2) DEFAULT 0,
  costAvoidance DECIMAL(15,2) DEFAULT 0,
  efficiencyGains DECIMAL(15,2) DEFAULT 0,
  totalBenefit DECIMAL(15,2) DEFAULT 0,
  netCashFlow DECIMAL(15,2) DEFAULT 0,
  cumulativeCashFlow DECIMAL(15,2) DEFAULT 0,
  projectedCI DECIMAL(5,2),
  projectedFCI DECIMAL(5,4),
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)
